### Layout Shell (MANDATORY)
<div class="flex justify-center items-start min-h-[calc(100dvh-100px)]">
  <div class="container mx-auto max-w-5xl bg-white rounded-lg lg:px-24 md:px-12 sm:px-6 pt-12 pb-12" id="content">
